<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{> template/title }}</title>
</head>
<body>
{{> template/header}}
<section class="main-intro">
    <div class="intro-top">
        <div class="main-text">
            <h2 class="text-title">여행을 쓰자,<br/>
                <span class="text-yolo">욜로</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-msg-wrapper">
          <span class="text-msg">
            여행의 소중한 순간을 욜로에 담아보세요. <br>
            메모, 사진 경로, 위치를 간편하게 작성하면, <br>
            욜로가 멋진 여행기를 만들어 드립니다.
          </span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="main-event">
            <img src="./img/banner-event.png">
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- db 연동해야할 부분 -->
    <ul class="main-tag">
        <li style="background-image: url(./img/holo.jpg)">
            <div class="dark-layer">
                #나홀로여행
            </div>
        </li>
        <li style="background-image: url(./img/eat.png)">
            <div class="dark-layer">
                #먹방여행
            </div>
        </li>
        <li style="background-image: url(./img/banner-tip.png)">
            <div class="dark-layer">
                욜로 사용법
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <!-- -->
</section>
<section class="main-mid">
    <ul class="main-mid-country">
        <!-- country.hbs -->
    </ul>
</section>
<section class="main-contents">
    <div class="main-contents-wrapper">
        <!-- contents db 연동 -->
    </div>
</section>
<section class="main-bottom">
    <div class="bottom-writer">
        <div class="bottom-writer-img-left"
             style="background-image: url(./img/rabbit.png)">
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-writer-text">
            당신도 지금 욜로에서 <span>여행작가</span>가 될 수 있습니다
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-writer-img-right"
             style="background-image: url(./img/airport.png)">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-wrapper">
        <div class="bottom-user-wrapper"
             style="transform: translate3d(260px, 0px, 0px);
             transition: 0.25s;">
            <ul class="bottom-user">
                <!-- userinfo.hbs db 연동해야함-->
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-prev">
            <img src="./img/go-left.png"/>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom-next">
            <img src="./img/go-right.png"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button class="go-top-btn">▲ TOP</button>
</section>
{{> template/footer}}
</body>
</html>
